item.title: How do i make teleport tabs?
item.dc:creator: @The_Reaper_X The Reaper X
item.description:
@The_Reaper_X wrote:

Look for case 185 in your client.java, that’s the actionpacket Rich is talking about. it’s a switch statement that uses Action Button Id’s as cases so that you can modify what you want to happen when you click the button, aka action button.
